Currently we are trying to use the ProfiledPID command from wpilib but are having issues with it.<br>
Link to command we have: <a href="https://github.com/WHS-FRC-3467/Skip-5.13/blob/master/src/main/java/frc/robot/subsystems/arm/ArmRioPID.java" rel="noopener nofollow ugc">https://github.com/WHS-FRC-3467/Skip-5.13/blob/master/src/main/java/frc/robot/subsystems/arm/ArmRioPID.java</a><br>
